{"tid":2410392,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人都係一嬲就會自自然然流眼淚","createTime":"2021-02-16T14:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T16:35:58.000Z","uid":10141,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a1403983adcae62ef7f38a5577b2c3c5578c9bd8","tid":2410392,"uid":10141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:29:43.000Z","msg":"由細到大都唔識表達嬲<br />\n<br />\n唔識嬲到面紅耳赤，反而一有少少嬲，就會自自然然咁流眼淚，然後就會喊<br />\n<br />\n又唔識鬧人，一開聲就會忍唔住聲都震埋，又開始喊<br />\n<br />\n男人老狗畀人話係喊包好柒，但我真係控制唔到啊嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a4f53d069d1c5f1eb6d4a0596421a6f7d79318","tid":2410392,"uid":201414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:31:01.000Z","msg":"一嬲就起機 冇曬霸氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ffbc32a5874986d8276deef8d8689b8aed0469","tid":2410392,"uid":186374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:31:39.000Z","msg":"我會<br />\n感性"},{"pid":"38fc0abb95625a98ad1b141530aadaf93eb0a312","tid":2410392,"uid":10208,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:31:58.000Z","msg":"好......好得意.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a61b2018f197e6a6f66235700e21ebd5cf7e91a8","tid":2410392,"uid":10141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38fc0abb95625a98ad1b141530aadaf93eb0a312","tid":2410392,"uid":10208,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:31:58.000Z","msg":"好......好得意.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:33:16.000Z","msg":"得咩意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一啲霸氣都冇<br />\n<br />\n想嬲又嬲唔到，又唔想人地當自己細路咁"},{"pid":"4627a43344b15facaca63f431c9cc6fef9756ece","tid":2410392,"uid":10141,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:33:59.000Z","msg":"因為一出聲就會喊<br />\n<br />\n只可以靜靜地唔出聲，谷鳩氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2dbc76ca96d7c2e98571108471cbd81b5267023","tid":2410392,"uid":367597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:36:28.000Z","msg":"我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"613a2a6d04a274356702a0184d5b76033e92946c","tid":2410392,"uid":386252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:44:38.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到好易喊咁"},{"pid":"ce50f5da8fdf0a74f22bd353034a9a88ee37448c","tid":2410392,"uid":350858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T15:07:20.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為咗唔想嚇親人 <br />\n比身邊嘅人以為自己無脾氣"},{"pid":"a5a02951ce3a60d90d0f1038d5be0f671bf58ccf","tid":2410392,"uid":235998,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T16:04:17.000Z","msg":"我都係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嬲得好緊要嘅話 一出聲就會聲都震埋然後開始流眼淚<br />\n最慘我係嬲緊嗰陣又好易笑返嘅人"},{"pid":"33d5ebde032b53266b3247c7654aa9cb0801d366","tid":2410392,"uid":370165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T16:12:54.000Z","msg":"我好易喊<br />\n隻眼好多水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f16cb760e6071feb5b784f88b07ffad3135acc9","tid":2410392,"uid":366802,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T17:18:43.000Z","msg":"明明內心好多嘢想講 想理論<br />\n但好似卡晒喺喉嚨<br />\n講出嚟完全唔係諗嗰回事<br />\n勁柒 冇晒霸氣又冇邏輯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f67c092cc3f321f4e538f6fdefe03fab881253f","tid":2410392,"uid":359398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T17:31:12.000Z","msg":"以前係 嬲個陣講多兩句就開始哽咽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但而加唔會 同人嘈交把聲都唔會震<br />\n可能比個社會迫到咁 人係要惡d"},{"pid":"4d16202f5522d9a0110600bf676423f515c0a284","tid":2410392,"uid":353749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4627a43344b15facaca63f431c9cc6fef9756ece","tid":2410392,"uid":10141,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:33:59.000Z","msg":"因為一出聲就會喊<br />\n<br />\n只可以靜靜地唔出聲，谷鳩氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T16:35:58.000Z","msg":"Same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"4627a43344b15facaca63f431c9cc6fef9756ece","tid":2410392,"uid":10141,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:33:59.000Z","msg":"因為一出聲就會喊<br />\n<br />\n只可以靜靜地唔出聲，谷鳩氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}